
---------------------------------------
|||| Scheduler PLugin Installation ||||
---------------------------------------


Default:
 - twister server side path: /opt/twister
 - twister client side path: /home/<username>/twister


	---- SERVER side ----

1. sudo cp /<twister_repository>/binaries/SchedulerPlugin/Scheduler/* /opt/twister/plugins

2. vim /home/<username>/twister/config/plugins.xml

append config:
<Plugin>
	<name>Scheduler</name>
	<jarfile>Scheduler.jar</jarfile>
	<pyfile>Scheduler.py</pyfile>
	<status>enabled</status>
</Plugin>


